Tangiwai
Homonym Number:  1
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:rail tragedy at Tangiwai on Christmas Eve, 1953, during Queen's visit, when a lahar from Mt Ruapehu destroyed a rail bridge with loss of 151 lives.
